        <div class="ba-head">
          <span class="ba-label">#9 · DAILY AUTOPILOT · $99/MO FLAT</span>
          <h3 class="ba-title">RankYak — Best daily content autopilot</h3>
          <p class="ba-sub">For publishers who want one article every day at a flat, predictable price.</p>
        </div>
        <p style="color: var(--text-2); margin: 0 0 20px;">RankYak delivers one article per day, every day, for a flat $99/month. No tiers, no add-ons. It handles keyword clustering, writing, and publishing to 9+ CMS platforms with Zapier and Make integrations. The platform launched in 2025 with a small team, limited reviews, and a backlink exchange that carries the same link scheme risk as Outrank. Good concept, limited track record.</p>
        <ul class="ba-list">
          <li><span class="ba-num">✓</span><div><h4>Flat-rate pricing — no surprises</h4><p>$99/month. One article daily. That's the whole offer.</p></div></li>
          <li><span class="ba-num">✓</span><div><h4>Consistent daily output across 9+ platforms</h4><p>Zapier and Make integrations extend to almost any CMS.</p></div></li>
          <li><span class="ba-num">✗</span><div><h4>Honest con: 2-person team, founded 2025, limited reviews</h4><p>Too new to trust for a primary content strategy. Backlink exchange is an additional risk.</p></div></li>
