          <span class="ba-label">#10 · HUMAN-QA AUTOPILOT · $149–$749/MO</span>
          <h3 class="ba-title">SEO.AI — Best autopilot with human review layer</h3>
          <p class="ba-sub">For businesses that want AI content speed with a human specialist checking every piece before it publishes.</p>
        </div>
        <p style="color: var(--text-2); margin: 0 0 20px;">SEO.AI adds a human SEO specialist review to every article before publishing — making it the only autopilot with a true quality gate. The trade-off: 4–8 articles per month at $18–$37 each. That's the lowest volume in the autopilot category at the highest per-article cost. If quality confidence matters more than volume, it's worth considering.</p>
        <ul class="ba-list">
          <li><span class="ba-num">✓</span><div><h4>Human specialist QA on every article</h4><p>Only autopilot with a built-in quality gate before content goes live.</p></div></li>
