          <h3 class="ba-title">Arvow — Best multilingual on-page automation</h3>
          <p class="ba-sub">For international sites that need 150+ language support and automated on-page SEO fixes.</p>
        </div>
        <p style="color: var(--text-2); margin: 0 0 20px;">Formerly Journalist AI, Arvow offers autoblogging in 150+ languages with on-page SEO agents that auto-fix schema, meta tags, internal linking, and alt text. It supports 9 CMS integrations, generates social posts from articles, and submits content directly to Google Search Console. Small team means spotty support, and content has factual accuracy issues on niche topics.</p>
        <ul class="ba-list">
          <li><span class="ba-num">✓</span><div><h4>Best language coverage in the category</h4><p>150+ languages. No other autopilot tool comes close for international publishing.</p></div></li>
          <li><span class="ba-num">✓</span><div><h4>On-page SEO agents auto-fix schema, meta, and linking</h4><p>Technical SEO and content automation in one platform.</p></div></li>
          <li><span class="ba-num">✗</span><div><h4>Honest con: factual accuracy issues on niche topics</h4><p>Spotty support and no brand voice control make it risky for sensitive verticals.</p></div></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
