        <p style="color: var(--text-2); margin: 0 0 20px;">Adaptify sits between software and agency. Weekly custom strategy, long-form content with E-E-A-T optimization, journalist-sourced backlinks, and a reporting dashboard. It's the most comprehensive option for agencies that can't build that stack themselves. At $499–$2,499/month, it's priced like a boutique agency. No schema support and limited CMS compatibility are notable gaps.</p>
        <ul class="ba-list">
          <li><span class="ba-num">✓</span><div><h4>Custom strategy updated weekly</h4><p>Journalist relationship-based backlinks included. Not a black-hat link farm.</p></div></li>
          <li><span class="ba-num">✓</span><div><h4>Google Analytics and Search Console integration</h4><p>Reporting connects to your existing data sources.</p></div></li>
          <li><span class="ba-num">✗</span><div><h4>Honest con: $499 minimum with limited CMS support and no schema</h4><p>Most small businesses don't need $499/month of managed services. And the missing schema support is a real gap.</p></div></li>
